1 medium onion
160g-200g diced salted chicken breast
1 tsp turmeric
1/4 tsp fresh ground black pepper


Fry the spices in a bit of olive oil; add the onions, then the chicken.
Fry on medium-high heat for a few minutes, then add about 200ml hot water. Cook for another 5 min.

Good served with green veg like broccoli or beans.

